OL,6,FIt would mean farmers have to plant
OL,7,F10% of their land with trees, and a
OL,8,Ffurther 10% would become habitat for
OL,9,Fwildlife in order to get government
OL,10,Fpayments to support their farms.
OL,12,FThis is, in part, to help the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment meet their own target of
OL,14,Fplanting 43,000 hectares of woodland
OL,15,Fby 2030.
