OL,3,CThousands of wellies line Senedd steps
OL,4,Cto protest new farming plans
OL,6,FThe latest protest has hit out at
OL,7,Fconcerns amongst farmers that the
OL,8,Fplan, in its current form, would
OL,9,Feffectively mean they have to give up
OL,10,Fa fifth of their land to help the
OL,11,Fenvironment.
OL,13,FAt the end of February, more than
OL,14,F3,000 protesters gathered outside the
OL,15,FSenedd to campaign against the scheme
OL,16,Fin the biggest protest in Senedd
OL,17,Fhistory.
OL,19,FA week later, today's protest has been
OL,20,Fdescribed by opposition politicians as
OL,21,F"poignant and powerful".
